# Keep the Docker build context lean and secret-free. The web image builds with
# the repo root as context; without this, every service's node_modules, .git, and
# any local .env would be shipped to the daemon (slow, and a leak risk).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example
**/coverage
**/*.log
docs
test
